Using the Nearby API and Firebase, view a special message on your devices. While most people will probably only have a couple phones or tablets, the ideal setup is using 11 different devices. Check out the video below to view the app in all of its awesomeness!

Prior to running this app for the first time, you'll need to get an API key for the Nearby API. Follow these instructions for setting up your key:
https://developers.google.com/nearby/messages/android/get-started

You will also need to add your Firebase URL in the Constants class.